graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    DSPO -->|pipeline execution| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines<br/>Tekton 1.8+]
    DSPO -->|platform services| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.9+<br/>Routes, OAuth, Service CA]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    DSPO -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus Operator]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    DSPO <-->|pipeline submission| NotebookController[Notebook Controller]
    DSPO -.->|model lineage| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]

    %% External Services (Optional - user-provided)
    DSPO -.->|metadata storage| ExternalDB[(External Database<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL)]
    DSPO -.->|artifact storage| ExternalS3[(External S3 Storage<br/>AWS/Compatible)]

    %% Default Optional Components (deployed by DSPO)
    DSPO -->|default metadata| MariaDB[(MariaDB 5.7+)]
    DSPO -->|default artifacts| Minio[(Minio<br/>S3-compatible)]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|displays UI| DSPO
    Dashboard -->|queries lineage| DSPO
    NotebookController -->|kfp-tekton SDK| DSPO
    ModelRegistry -.->|MLMD gRPC| DSPO

    %% Tekton Relationship Detail
    DSPO -->|creates/watches| TektonResources[Tekton Resources:<br/>PipelineRuns, TaskRuns,<br/>CustomRuns, PipelineLoops]
    TektonResources -.->|part of| Tekton

    %% OpenShift Services Detail
    OpenShift -->|provides| Routes[Routes]
    OpenShift -->|provides| OAuth[OAuth 2.0]
    OpenShift -->|provides| ServiceCA[Service CA]
    DSPO -->|uses| Routes
    DSPO -->|uses| OAuth
    DSPO -->|uses| ServiceCA

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff
    style Tekton fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style OpenShift fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Prometheus fill:#e8743b,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style NotebookController fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ExternalDB fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#000
    style ExternalS3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5,color:#000
    style MariaDB fill:#d0e0e3,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Minio fill:#d0e0e3,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style TektonResources fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#000
    style Routes fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#000
    style OAuth fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#000
    style ServiceCA fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#000

    %% Legend
    subgraph Legend
        Required[Required Dependency]
        Optional[Optional Dependency]
        Internal[Internal ODH Component]
        External[External Service]
    end

    style Required fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Optional fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Internal fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style External fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
